description:
On this edition of Jackan O'Brien Needs A Friend Jack and Miles discuss Rick Santorum dismissing Native American Culture entirely, Farmer John no longer making Dodger Dogs, bringing Tony Stark back to life, the Supreme Court deciding whether or not Americans should be MORE heavily armed, ANOTHER police killing of an unarmed black man, and Sharks getting freaky.
